      "content": {
        "parts": [
          {
            "text": "Here are some med spas and clinics in Katy, TX, that offer anti-aging facial treatments:\n\n*   **Le Chloé Med Spa:** Specializes in non-surgical anti-aging treatments using cutting-edge technology to rejuvenate skin, smooth fine lines, and firm areas of concern. They offer treatments like PDO threads, neck tightening, brow lifts, and hand rejuvenation, all customized to individual needs. They also offer free consultations.\n*   **4Ever Young Anti-aging Clinic and Medical Spa:** Offers PRP (platelet-rich plasma) facials to rejuvenate skin by stimulating cellular healing and collagen production. This treatment aims to address fine lines, wrinkles, and dullness.\n*   **Viata Aesthetics and Wellness:** Provides aesthetic services, including Botox and fillers, to restore a youthful appearance. They offer Botox and Dysport, and use dermal fillers to treat wrinkles, fine lines, volume loss, and sagging skin.\n*   **Spavia Cinco Ranch:** Offers facials and skincare treatments, including an Age Defense Facial infused with Vitamin C and hyaluronic acid to nourish and plump the skin. They also offer a Hydraderm facial with diamond tone microdermabrasion and a Platinum Ice & Glow Facial.\n*   **Katy Medi Spa:** Offers advanced skincare treatments, including facials, chemical peels, skin resurfacing, and photofacials (IPL).\n*   **Face to Face Spa:** Provides facials designed to address a range of concerns, including softening the appearance of aging. They offer classic facials, Hydrafacials, chemical peels, microneedling, microdermabrasion, and dermaplaning. New clients can get a premium medi-facial with a choice of chemical peel or microdermabrasion for a special price.\n*   **H-Town Aesthetics:** Offers personalized treatments to help clients achieve a refreshed, youthful appearance. Services include Botox, dermal fillers, PRP and PRF treatments, laser hair removal, and microneedling.\n*   **Ageless Med Spa:** Offers various types of facials to meet specific skin needs, including traditional facials, IPL facials, HydraFacials, and chemical peels.\n*   **MedSpa At Villagio:** Provides medical spa treatments, salon services, and day spa experiences, including laser hair removal, Botox, and microneedling.\n*   **LUXE Medical Aesthetics:** Combines cutting-edge techniques and professional care with high-quality products to protect, revitalize, and nurture the skin.\n\n"
          }
        ],
